只有您有此密码的获取权限。

此密码具备较高的安全强度，若需要使用该密码，可直接复制并粘贴到密码输入框，并务必备份好该密码。
en:
The generated password was created by your browser, locally.

No one but you can access it.

Please paste it below and save a copy in a safe place.

zh-cn:
这是你所有资产的估值，包含了在界面中设置了隐藏的资产、委单中的资产、债仓及抵押物。

估值采用实时获得的区块链上的价格，可能不那么精确。
en:
This is the estimated value of all your assets, including any hidden assets, open orders, debt and collateral.

Estimation is using only live blockchain data and may not be perfectly accurate.

zh-cn: 密码必须至少包含12位字符
en: Password must be at least 12 characters

en: Password must contain upper case, lower case, numbers and special characters

en: Account name should not contain continuous dashes

zh-cn: 账户名必须以小写字母或数字结尾

en: Account name should only contain lowercase letters, dashes, or numbers

zh-cn: 我已经充分地知晓并理解，如果忘记密码，没有任何人能够帮助我恢复
en: I understand that no one can recover my password if I lose or forget it

zh-cn: 我已经写下或用其他方式妥善保存了我的密码
en: I have written down or otherwise stored my password

en: I really want to logout, and I know what I am doing

zh-cn: 云钱包模式在创建和登录时即时使用您提供的密码和账户名衍生出私钥，因此在同一时间只能登录一个Cybex账户。
en: The cloud wallet uses a password in combination with your account name to generate your private keys on the fly. It restricts you to only logging in with one account at a time, in return for ease of use and convenience.

zh-cn: 为了保障您的资产安全，我们推荐您使用20位以上的长密码，您可以使用系统推荐密码获得一个随机长密码。
en: We highly recommed to use password with more than 20 characters for the safety of your digital assets, you can easily get an appropriate password through our "Use Generated Password" section.

zh-cn: 你可以从任何地方登录自己的账户，包括了不同的电脑、不同的浏览器，只需要账户名和密码。但请务必使用一个较为安全的密码
en: The cloud wallet lets you login to your wallet from anywhere using only your account name and password, but a strong password is highly recommended!

zh-cn: 点击下方按钮前往交易所开始交易
en: Click the button below to start exploring.

zh-cn: 请仔细阅读下面的说明并确认您已理解全部内容。点击“登出”按钮，您的账户信息将会被清除。
en: Please read and confirm the statments below carefully, then click the 'Logout' button, the browser will reload current page. Your account information will be erased.

en: Both a Tag and an Address are required to successfully deposit your XRP to Cybex
